  Copyright 2003, R. Barrie Slaymaker, Jr., All Rights Reserved
  
  =head1 LICENSE
  
  You may use this module under the terms of the BSD, Artistic, or GPL licenses,
  any version.
  
  =head1 AUTHOR
  
  Barrie Slaymaker E<lt>C<barries@slaysys.com>E<gt>
  
